	<h1 class="title">《烈日灼心》成了曹保平最卖座的电影，他说下一次还想把故事拍得更清楚些</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">刘平安 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-15 16:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14911/medium/14911.jpg?1442255928" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="14911" data-title="《《烈日灼心》成了曹保平最卖座的电影，他说下一次还想把故事拍得更清楚些》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/14911/medium/14911.jpg?1442255928" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/14911.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
